    "texte_orig": "No...[SP]If[SP]you[SP]quit[SP]being[SP]Boss...[SP]What's[SP]going[SP]to\nhappen[SP]to[SP]this[SP]school?[SP]To[SP]us?[1205][U+000F][SP]Who's[SP]going[SP]to\ntake[SP]care[SP]of[SP]everything?",
